headline: Nvidia, chip stocks jump after Trump says some chipmakers exempt from 100% semiconductor tariff
summary: Nvidia and other stocks climbed on Thursday after President Trump said he'll exempt companies from his planned semiconductor tariffs if they have committed to making their chips in the US.
